API - Annotation Type in org.apiguardian
@API is used to annotate public types, methods, constructors, and fields within a framework or application in order to indicate their level of stability and how they are intended to be used by consumers of the API.
API.Status - Enum in org.apiguardian
Indicates the status of an API element and therefore its level of stability as well.
